main.message: Turning ideas into code and dreams into reality.
main.aboutMe: I am Caio Henrique Rodrigues, a 22 years old full-stack developer currently in the final year of the Information Systems program at Unifafibe University. My initial education in System Development at Etec Bebedouro provided me with a strong foundation in the field. I am looking for opportunities to expand my knowledge and tackle new challenges. My passion for technology and innovation drives me to seek creative and high-quality solutions. Currently, I work as a full-stack developer and am eager to contribute to projects that challenge my skills and offer significant impact.
